On this edition of the Tampa Bay Zeitning Jack and Miles discuss National Radio Day, Chris Webber throwing shade, Stephen Miller called Obama the worst president of all time, it's Amy Adams birthday, and Putin opponent Alexei Navalny had their tea poisoned.
